'''Keben Park''' was a park in [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]], overlooking the Presidential residence and other government offices. It contained artificial hills that were used for [[board-skiing]] during the snow season. [[Glider (creature)|Gliders]] were known to inhabit this park.

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] visited there in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], planning to [[Assassination of Thrackan Sal-Solo|assassinate]] [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]]. While planning, he ate [[breadstick]]s and fed the crumbs to nearby gliders.

It was here that Solo was ambushed by [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] and [[Mirta Gev]]. The three discussed the assassination of Thrackan, and Han revealed to Fett that [[Ailyn Vel]] had been captured by [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo's]] [[Galactic Alliance Guard]]. In turn, Fett revealed to Han that Ailyn was his daughter.

